headline: Steadfast and Strong: Invest in These 2 Durable American Giants
summary: Betting against the United States when it comes to business has been a mistake.  American Express is a beneficiary of continued economic growth in the United States.  Amazon has spent hundreds of millions on infrastructure, with much of that in the U.S.
